labels.name: A-diagnostics

labels.name: T-compiler

body:
Does not appear on Stable or Beta in the playground.

```rust
fn main() {}

fn foo() {
    let something = 0;
    if somehting % 8 == 0 {}
}
```

([Playground](https://play.rust-lang.org/?version=nightly&mode=debug&edition=2018&gist=f4320f4b1710b2a96271d5c1726224d1))

Errors:

```
   Compiling playground v0.0.1 (/playground)
error[E0425]: cannot find value `somehting` in this scope
 --> src/main.rs:7:8
  |
7 |     if somehting % 8 == 0 {}
  |        ^^^^^^^^^ help: a local variable with a similar name exists: `something`
```
